description.content:
Hello

I've got plenty of experience in the field, and my goal is to create affordable, fast, and unique websites that really shine.


What We Offer:


  • Professional and Attention-Grabbing WordPress Websites.
  • Responsive on All Devices.
  • Fast Loading, Secure, and Optimized for SEO.
  • Licensed Images.
  • Optimized Image Sliders, Popups, and CTAs for Higher Conversions.
  • Connecting with Email Marketing Platforms 
  • Integration with Social Media Platforms
  • User-Friendly Page Builder Editor.


All-in-One Starter Website

This package offers a complete 1-page website, featuring UI design and development, minimalist copy, SEO, hosting setup, and training.


Web Pro Package

Starter package + 4 additional pages. This option introduces animations and a CMS for effortless content management and updates.


Web Master Package

Building on Web Pro + 3 additional pages, this incorporates marketing tools, e-commerce functionality, and analytics setup


WHY CHOOSE US?


  1. Innovative Design
  2. Support After Sale.
  3. Client Satisfaction
  4. Highly Skilled in Web Development
  5. Years of Web Development Experience


Feel free to send me a message to chat about your unique project.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What do I need before we start?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: First, you need to buy a domain and hosting. If you haven't, we can help. We also require your company logo (optional) and the page names for your website, like Home, About Us, Services, and Contact. You'll provide content (text and images) for these pages.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you offer domain and hosting services?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: No, we don't. We recommend using HostGator or Bluehost for hosting.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will you make my website live on our hosting?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, but you'll need to give us your credentials.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you offer revisions?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, we offer multiple revisions within the project's scope. Your satisfaction is our top priority.!

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can I easily manage my website from the admin panel without programming knowledge?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, you can easily add, update, delete, and maintain your website from the admin panel. We'll provide the username and password.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will my website be mobile-friendly?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, it will be responsive on all devices.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will my website be SEO-friendly?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, the basic structure of your website will be SEO-friendly.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can I see samples of your work?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: You can message us to see our work samples.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide content writing services for the website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: No, you'll need to provide the content.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you offer support after completing the job?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, we provide free support based on your package. Details are in our gig's packages. You can reach out even after the project is finished.

reviews.comment:
The development of the website has been a great journey overall, though it took some time to get to the polished result we have now. There were multiple people involved in this project, which unfortunately led to frequent miscommunication. Despite providing clear and detailed instructions, some points were overlooked during the process.

Additionally, there were certain aspects of the website that I had to suggest, as I assumed Michael and his team would already have considered them. This was a bit surprising, given their expertise. However, after I requested a Zoom meeting to address these concerns, communication improved significantly, and the team was able to make progress more efficient.

seller_response.comment: Thank you for your valuable feedback! There was a slight delay in our response as we allocate dedicated time to each project before transitioning to the next one. When a different developer takes over, it can make things a bit challenging, as we often have to wait weeks to receive her feedback.

reviews.comment: Working with Michael was a great experience. Although we had a rough start due to my initial lack of clear communication about my vision for the site, once we got on the same page, he worked diligently. Michael delivered the final site design in just two days and had it published within hours. I would definitely do business with him again.

Best regards,
